    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（そう、視線をステージに戻した時）\n（さくらの目が、俺に訴えかけてきた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(That's right‚ when I turned my gaze back to the stage)\n(Sakura's eyes appealed to me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "（{user}さん、心配しないで）\n（私達なら大丈夫です）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Manager-san‚ don't worry.)\n(We'll be fine.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（さくら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Sakura…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 25.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 29.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "（ここにいる私達は、独りじゃないから）\n（自分がやるべきって思ったことを、やって下さい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We're not alone here.)\n(Do what you think you should do.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（……よし）\n（なんとかしてみせるから、待っててくれ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…Alright.)\n(I'll do something‚ so wait for me!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 39.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 39.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 39.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "直せないって……\nそれ、どういう意味ですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can't fix it…?\nWhat do you mean!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どう、と言われてもね～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you want me to do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3333334000004,
          "startTime": 48.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、大丈夫か？　復旧の目処は立ったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is everyone okay? Have you figured out how to fix it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 52.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……！\nさくら達は、大丈夫なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san…!\nAre Sakura and the others okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。むしろ、背中を押されちゃったよ\nそれより、状況は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Actually‚ they encouraged me.\nWhat's the situation?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 63.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "それが……機材トラブルが深刻で\nサニピのステージ中の復旧は無理だろうって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… the equipment trouble is serious‚ and\nthey said it's impossible to fix it during Sunny Peace's stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 70.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なぜですか？\nリハの時はなんの問題もありませんでしたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why?\nThere weren't any problems during the rehearsal‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうなんだけどね～……どうしてかな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true‚ but～… I wonder why～…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "元々、あまり機材の調子も良くなかったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The equipment wasn't in good condition to begin with…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 82.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "貴方達……それでもプロなの？\n自分の仕事には責任持ちなさいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You… and you call yourselves professionals?\nTake responsibility for your own work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 88.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（……さては、姫野さんに買収でもされたんだな）\n（サニピの持ち時間が終わるまで、しらを切るつもりか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…I bet she bribed them.)\n(She's planning to play dumb until Sunny Peace's time is up.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 95.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "せめて、ラスサビだけでもいい……\n音を流して下さい。復旧を急いで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At least let the last chorus play…\nPlease turn on the sound. Hurry up and fix it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そう言われてもね～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you say that～…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "不調の原因が分からないことには、何も出来ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't do anything until I know what's causing the problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 110.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（くそ……もう時間はないぞ）\n（何か……何か手はないのか……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Damn it… We're running out of time.)\n(Something… Is there anything I can do…!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 116.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら達の声……\nマイク、直ったみたいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura and the others' voices…\nThe mics seem to be working again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えっ……な、なんでだ！　直るはずは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…? Wh-why!? It shouldn't be working…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 124.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 124.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なんで？　直るはずは？　どういうことですか？\n単に、機材が復旧しただけですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why? It shouldn't be working? What do you mean?\nIt simply means the equipment has recovered‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 131.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり……\n故障に見せかけて、意図的に妨害してたんですね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As I thought…\nYou intentionally sabotaged it to make it look like a malfunction‚ didn't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
